<h1>How to Play The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild on a Computer</h1>

<img src="https://i2-prod.dailystar.co.uk/tech/gaming/article22152488.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200b/1_BotW_Screen04.png">

<p>Breath of the Wild is a huge open-world game made by Nintendo for the Switch and Wii U. The game has an amazing story, combat, and more. 
This game is a Nintendo exclusive, which is very problematic for a lot of people who want to play the game. However, there is a solution to 
this problem. You can actually use a Wii U emulator to run this game on any capable computer, but this tutorial is mostly just for PC users.</p>
